```

This will:
- Create your first commit
- Save `cal.sh` to the repository history

---

## ğŸ§  Notes

- To unstage `cal.sh`:  
  ```bash
  git rm --cached cal.sh
  ```

- To track other files:  
  ```bash
  git add <filename>
  ```

- To add everything:  
  ```bash
  git add .
  ```

